        with our NFC activation, rarity infrastructure, archive system, and collector-facing storefront.
      </p>
      <div class="cc-btn-row">
        <a class="cc-btn cc-btn--gold" href="#CollaborateContact-{{ section.id }}">Apply to collaborate</a>
        <a class="cc-btn cc-btn--outline" href="#CollaborateHow-{{ section.id }}">How it works</a>
