        <button class="cc-tab-button" type="button" role="tab" aria-selected="false" data-target="collective">Collectives</button>
        <button class="cc-tab-button" type="button" role="tab" aria-selected="false" data-target="gallery">Galleries</button>
      </div>

      <div class="cc-tab-panels">
        <div class="cc-tab-panel is-active" data-panel="artist">
          <div class="cc-panel-card">
            <h3 class="cc-panel-title">For independent <em>artists</em></h3>
            <div class="cc-copy" style="margin-bottom:3.2rem;">Create a small or mid-size IRIS drop with your own visual language while we handle the operational layer.</div>
            <ul class="cc-panel-list">
              <li>Develop a signed edition concept that fits the IRIS format.</li>
              <li>Sell through our storefront with your collection presented on-platform.</li>
              <li>Each collector receives activation, passport, and archive visibility.</li>
              <li>You focus on the work. We support launch, logistics, and buyer flow.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="cc-panel-visual">
            <div class="cc-panel-tag">Independent launch</div>
            <div class="cc-panel-metric">
              <div class="cc-panel-big">50</div>
              <div class="cc-panel-label">Suggested starting edition</div>
            </div>
            <div class="cc-panel-example"><strong>Ideal for</strong>First IRIS release, artist-led concept drop, audience building.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="cc-tab-panel" data-panel="collective">
          <div class="cc-panel-card">
